Slides
=======
* Title slide
    - Specific
        - Different background
* What is generative AI slide
    - General
        - Make more interactive
        - Separate into different slides per modality
    - Specific
        - Generative text->text models
            * Ask students if they know what the technical term for these is? A: LLMs (large langugage models)
            * Show mock chatbot
                - User typing something in
                - LLM responding
            * Animate in names/logos of different chatbots at the bottom
                - ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini
        - Generative text->image models, text->video models
            * Ask students if they know what the technical term for these is? A: Typically, diffusion models (image diffusion, video diffusion)
            * Show mock chatbot
                - User typing something in
                - Diffusion model generating an image
                - Also show diffusion model generating a video
            * Animate in names/logos of different image diffusion models at the bottom
                - Midjourney, Sora
* Benefits and dangers slide
    - Visual examples of...
        * Fake articles/images
        * Why it's a useful tool
            - Coding/making software
        * But emphasize that it can be wrong
* CLIP slide
    - Less jargon

